  m_text: '1. Information We Collect

    Personal Information:

    Device Information:
    [IP Address, Device Type, Android Version, Advertising ID (GAID)].

    Usage
    Data: [Playtime, game progress, app crashes/crash reports].

    2. How We Use
    the Information

    To provide and maintain game features.

    To analyze performance
    and fix technical issues via [Google Analytics/Firebase].

    To display relevant
    advertisements through [AdMob/Unity Ads].

    3. Data Sharing with Third Parties

    We
    may share data with service providers such as:

    Google Play Services: To
    store game progress and achievements.

    Advertising Partners: To personalize
    the advertising experience.

    4. Data Security

    We implement standard
    security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access.

    5.
    User Rights

    You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion
    of your personal data by contacting us at the email address provided below.

    6.
    Children''s Privacy

    This application [does not collect/collects in a controlled
    manner] information from children under the age of 13, in compliance with Google
    Play policies.

    7. Contact Information

    Email: NOTYET'
